    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 12,044₽ | 物品价值: 3,819 | Mechanic报价: 2,139₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 4,965₽\n购买渠道 @ Peacekeeper 等级1 < 34$ ≈ 4,098₽\n\n220-239式照门式导轨是Sight Mount公司为西格-绍尔220、226、227、229、239型手枪生产的。它可替代原有标准照门并且可以在未安装瞄准镜的情况下使用。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 12,044₽ | 物品价值: 3,819 | Mechanic报价: 2,139₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 4,965₽\n购买渠道 @ Peacekeeper 等级1 < 34$ ≈ 4,098₽\n\nThe 220-239 rear sight bearing manufactured by Sight Mount for SIG Sauer 220, 226, 227, 229, 239 pistols. It is installed as a replacement of the standard rear sight and allows to use it even if no scope is installed."
